    Custom Reactions

    .addcustreact / .acr

    Add a custom reaction with a trigger and a response.

    .editcustreact / .ecr

    Edits the custom reaction's response given its ID.
    .listcustreact / .lcr

    Lists global or server custom reactions (20 commands per page) grouped by trigger

    .showcustreact / .scr

    Shows a custom reaction's response on a given ID.
    .delcustreact / .dcr

    Deletes a custom reaction on a specific index.
